- **[High confidence]** [`execution/agents/library/factual/navier-stokes/vasseur-de-giorgi/non-cz-pressure-routes-tool-independence.md`](/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-atlas/execution/agents/library/factual/navier-stokes/vasseur-de-giorgi/non-cz-pressure-routes-tool-independence.md) is the best local statement of why the barrier is structural:
