+### 6.7 Exact notation map between the toy circuit and the shell cascade
+
+- [VERIFIED] The shell-level identification is
+
+  ```text
+  a   <-> X1,n
+  b   <-> X2,n
+  c   <-> X3,n
+  d   <-> X4,n
