+### 6.8 Layer 3: The final blowup mechanism
+
+- [VERIFIED] Proposition 6.3 produces checkpoint times and amplitudes
+
+  ```text
+  0 <= t_n0 < t_n0+1 < ... < t_N,
+  e_n0, ..., e_N > 0
