+### 6.9 Why finite-time blowup follows
+
+- [VERIFIED] Since `e_n` stays comparable from one scale to the next, the lifespan estimate gives
+
+  ```text
+  t_n - t_{n-1} <= C (1 + ε0)^(-(5/2 - 1/100) n),
