+
+  with equations
+
+  ```text
+  ∂t a  = -ε^(-2) c d - ε a b - ε^2 exp(-K^10) a c,
+  ∂t b  =  ε a^2 - ε^(-1) K^10 c^2,
+  ∂t c  =  ε^2 exp(-K^10) a^2 + ε^(-1) K^10 b c,
+  ∂t d  =  ε^(-2) c a - K d ã,
+  ∂t ã  =  K d^2,
+  ```
+
+  with initial data
+
+  ```text
+  a(0)=1,
+  b(0)=c(0)=d(0)=ã(0)=0.
+  ```
